Our group is focusing on the effects of deforestaion and how the goverment is regulating the process of clearing land for farming. Our group found multiple soucres relating to goverment polices and regulations that a number of orginizations are trying to enforce. Our Groups question is why are most goverment orginizations avoiding this large scale deforestion for profit. The Farmers in the area are mostly farming soy or cattle to turn a quick profit at the expense of most of the world's oxygen.
